text: Eastwood, Victoria is a residential suburb of Bairnsdale in the East Gippsland region of Victoria in Australia.http://services.land.vic.gov.au/maps/interactive.jsphttp://www.eastgippsland.vic.gov.au/files/content/public/plans_and_projects/plans_for_towns_and_localities/bairnsdale/13/volume_1_bairnsdale_growth_strategy.pdfhttp://www.censusdata.abs.gov.au/census_services/getproduct/census/2011/quickstat/SSC20438?opendocument&navpos;=220 At the 2016 census Eastwood had a population of 2,766 people https://quickstats.censusdata.abs.gov.au/census_services/getproduct/census/2016/quickstat/SSC20830?opendocument == References == Category:East Gippsland
